gauravaṃ ārādhyeṣu cittasya namratā. tābhyāṃ saha vartate. salajjaṃ pūrvavat. sabhayaṃ skhalitam ālokya bhītam. śāntaṃ saṃyatendriyam, sattvārādhanayatnavat.

<commentary>yad ekasya rucijanakaṃ tad anyasya viparītam. anyonyaviruddhābhiḥ pṛthagjanecchābhirakheditam avipratisāri. katham? dayānvitam. hetupadam etat. kutaḥ? yasmāt kleśotpādān na svātantryādidam etat parasparaviruddhacaritam eṣāṃ bālānām iti matvā.</commentary>

